          "type": "htmlBlock",
          "title": "Safety and Health Orientation Sign in Log",
          "html": "<p>Rev. **** 3 | Effective: **** 04/07/2026 | Safety Officer: Matt Ramsey</p>\n<p>ACKNOWLEDGMENT</p>\n<p>This policy outlines the essential safety and health procedures for all personnel operating within MH Construction job sites. Adherence to these guidelines is critical for maintaining a safe working environment and preventing accidents. All employees are required to familiarize themselves with these procedures to ensure compliance with regulatory standards. [Section Title] Policy is designed to protect our workforce and ensure operational excellence.</p>\n<p>I acknowledge that I have read, understand, and agree to comply with the MH Construction [Section Title] Policy as required by 29 and WAC.</p>\n<p>TRAINING / MEETING LOG</p>\n<table class=\"sec-data-table first-row-header\"><tr><td><p>Topic/Subject</p></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><p>Trainer/Presenter</p></td><td></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td></tr></table>"
        },
